{"word":"G5562 - χωρέω - chōréō - kho-reh'-o - Come","sections":[{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">χωρέω</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong><span class=\"transliteration\">chōréō</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong><span class=\"phonetic\">kho-reh'-o</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong><span class=\"short-definition\">Come</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>இலக்கண சொல்வகை / Part(s) of speech: </strong>Verb / வினைச்சொல்</span>"},{"paragraph":"வினைச்சொல் - ஏற்றுக்கொள், இடங்கொடு"},{"paragraph":"1. to leave a space"},{"paragraph":"2. to go forward, advance, proceed"},{"paragraph":"3. to have space or room for receiving or holding something"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English: </strong>From <a href=\"#/G5561 - χώρα - chṓra - kho'-rah/5561\">G5561</a>; to <i>be</i> in (<i>give</i>) <i>space</i>, that is, (intransitively) to <i>pass</i>, <i>enter</i>, or (transitively) to <i>hold</i>, <i>admit</i> (literally or figuratively): - come, contain, go, have, place, (can, be room to) receive.</span>"},{"paragraph":""}]}